受既資源又少左<br />\n仲有軍事呢d 唔係大國真係自保就夠<br />\n因為小國好大機會用唔著<br />\n你又唔會想佢想用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好似沖繩等地D居民都唔係好鍾意美軍駐守<br />\n過幾年又一單强姦又盛, 你話有事都係指意美國, 咁某程度上呢D係代價<br />\n再加上其他各方面多少要濕下美國<br />\n呢條數值唔值真係要問安倍<br />\n<br />\n反而想睇下解禁後日本軍備可以玩到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 係我認我係花生友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c52604173743664e53580f7631d465fd590e0f3","tid":297314,"uid":35347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"其實改個名就得啦<br />\n乜仲有人覺得而家自衛隊渣過普通軍隊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19e41926bde9dfc135e19cd20f73f8a6deb03b5","tid":297314,"uid":121496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"大大個軍國主義國家就係隔離，有人反對的話一定係左膠上腦"},{"pid":"00047a790d3c6f78dc4e7e5c8db7ce60fc5a8eef","tid":297314,"uid":23832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但修憲建議已遭受鄰國中國和南韓抨擊，也勾起許多人對二戰期間日本皇軍侵略暴行的痛苦回憶，<span style=\"color: red;\">也有人擔心日本軍國主義復辟，對鄰國構成威脅。</span><br />\n<br />\n年年閱兵最撚軍國主義嗰個走去話人復辟軍國主義   人唔笑狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8c2968164c94a89056827c9b30dac9e3ed839eed","tid":297314,"uid":40216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌德國得點解日本唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國比美國駐軍 何來有軍隊</blockquote><br />\n&lt;a href=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.bundeswehr.de/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bundeswehr.de%2F&d=9H99dlmJ%2Bs6KO3W%2FO%2Bp%2B8v755KD0hvc